        <h2>Solving Linear Equations</h2>

        <p>
            A linear equation is an equation that forms a straight line when graphed.
            Example:
        </p>

        <p><strong>2x + 6 = 14</strong></p>

        <h3>Steps to Solve:</h3>
        <ol>
            <li>Subtract 6 from both sides → 2x = 8</li>
            <li>Divide both sides by 2 → x = 4</li>
        </ol>

        <button id="actionBtn">Check Answer</button>
        <p id="message"></p>
